              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "REAC"
                ],
                "institute": "1CANCRC"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "  heavy water moderated, light water",
                "cooled, nuclear research reactor (NRX) at the Can.",
                "                              Chalk River Laboratories"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two long irradiations were carried out:",
                "1. approximately 10 mg of spectroscopically pure Cs2CO3",
                "in the M.T.R., for 140 days.",
                "2. approximately 10 mg of CsNO3 in the NRX reactor,",
                "for 356 days. Two short irradiations were made, each",
                "of 16 hr. using a position in NRX similar to that used",
                "for the long irradiation. For these irradiations the",
                "cesium compounds which were of spectroscopic purity,",
                "were dried at 110.C and weighed into silica tubes which",
                "were then sealed. CsC1, 36.8 mg, was used in the first",
                "irradiation and Cs2CO3, 32.1 mg, in the second."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "D4PI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The Beta-counter was of conventional 4Pi design,",
                " using methane as counting gas."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The monitors were irradiated in the same",
                "capsule as the cesium samples and then, after a",
                "decay period of 5 days the 60Co activity was measured",
                "in an ionization chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
